Swatch Revenue Will ‘Exceed’ SF7 Billion in 2011, NZZ Says

-- B y   D e r m o t   D o h e r t y
-- 
2011-10-23T10:19:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-23/swatch-revenue-will-exceed-sf7-billion-in-2011-nzz-says.html
Swatch Group AG (UHR) ’s sales this year
will “clearly exceed” 7 billion Swiss francs ($7.9 billion),
while growth adjusted for currency swings may reach 9 percent to
11 percent in 2012,  NZZ  am Sonntag reported, citing Chief
Executive Officer Nick Hayek.  September was the watchmaker’s strongest-ever month, Hayek
said, according to the report in today’s newspaper. The company
has never had such a large order backlog, NZZ said, citing
Hayek.  To contact the reporter on this story:
